title: Larrymania
overview: Larry Hernandez and family are back for a sixth season with cameras capturing their ups and downs as they navigate life in Larrymania. Last year, the world saw Larry face true hardship, but this only strengthened the bond with his family who supported him through his darkest moments. This year will be the year of new beginnings, for him and his entire family. Larry will find himself embracing the new freedoms in his life, releasing new music, and contemplating life-long commitments.
